name: Trey Green (self-titled) (CD)
description: "Trey Green mixes observations inane and insane with poignant moment and memorable arrangements on his self-titled debut CD. The end result is a journey through madness with the occasional foothold on sanity; creating a highly entertaining if off-kilter musical experience. Trey Green isn't afraid to just be who he is on CD and let you judge him on the merits. The end result is glorious insanity, the kind you run into every single day in the real world, but with a touch of humor and panache. A joyous romp through Green's Id without safety nets. A must-hear." - Wildy's World

name: Awesome Shot Glass
description: These shot glasses are currently empty.  When you buy one, you simply fill it with the tequila of your choice to make it temporarily full.  Unless you're under 21, in which case, you'll need to go to Mexico to legally fill it with tequila.
